      <section id="id11341582">
        <title>Chapter 4</title>
        <para id="id11577124">This went on for a long time.</para>
        <para id="id4575407">The shoemaker and his wife were never hungry.</para>
        <para id="id12710872">One night the shoemaker’s wife said, “Let’s sit up and find out who makes our shoes”.</para>
        <para id="id5481767">And so they did.</para>
        <para id="id12710878">When the clock struck twelve, three little elves ran into the room. They jumped onto the workbench.</para>
        <para id="id11126985">They rapped and tapped and made all the shoes. Then they ran away.</para>
